Go to iis manager.
right click BPWEN-PC\hwang822\Sites\Add FDP sites...
FTP Site Name: Default Ftp Site. 
Content Directory: C:\inetpub\wwwroot. (could be any where, set C:\inetpub\wwwroot to remote update web codes).
Next
Binding IP Address: 192.168.0.109, Port: 21.
Check Start FTP site autmatically.
SSL: No SSL
Next.
Authentication: Basic. Allow access: Apecified users (default using system user username and password).
